text: Your series with photos titled 'toy camera' effect and Rainbow tree is really cool! I also really like the one titled "Beauty everywhere". You have good sense of strong silhouette in many of your photos, like the aptly named "Silhouette flowers", but also in some of the more subtle ones like the overhanging leaves in "raging waters" and trees in "Carisbrooke castle (I love the light in that one too).Strong silhouette is a really important concept for animation :slightly_smiling_face: Your animal photos are great too! Did you take those at the zoo?
How did your interviews go last week?
